Doc File for Game Source
************************

1. All Objects are Interleaved Bobs(No Sprites)
2. All Objects have X,Y
3. Collisions between objects = Box Method
4. Alien movement/speed depends on number remaining
5. Alien fire triggered by MM's random number generator
5. Or when 4 or less remain
6. Each Bob has it's own flag to decide
a) When its been hit
b) If Hit Which animation number to use
c) Whether to fire missile if not hit
d) If fired missile is in motion
7. Bonus Alien appears depending on number of hits

Sorry to keep it so short but I hate typing in doc files
Hope you all enjoy the game...............
					  Blaine
